Class ImageGenerated

  • java.lang.Object
    • SupavisioJ.ImageGenerated.ImageGenerated

  • public class ImageGenerated
extends java.lang.Object
    Class ImageGenerated handles the data retrieved from spectra in order to generate an image from a spectra portion.
